{"lemma":"كَرِّ","slug":"كَرِّ","root":"ك.ر.ر","root_slug":"ك-ر-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ك-ر-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":8},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n36801","n36802"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%83%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to return, to come back, to recur, to head back"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to return to attack again, to assail"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of كَرَّ (karra) (form I); return, coming back, head back"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of كَرَّ (karra) (form I); attack"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"rope woven from palm bast or fibres"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a dry measure, six ass loads; 60 قَفِيز (qafīz), 2700 kg","tags":["obsolete"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a dry measure, six ass loads; 120 قَفِيز (qafīz), 2880 kg","tags":["obsolete"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"the foal of an ass","tags":["dialectal","obsolete"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Ultimately from Akkadian 𒄀𒆤𒈣 (/⁠kuru⁠/, “short reed mat, collection of reeds; a woven thing”), from Sumerian 𒄥 (gur, “to twist, to wind, to turn”).\n\nBorrowed from Aramaic כּוֹרָא (kōrā, “a dry measure”), Classical Syriac ܟܘܪܐ (kōrā, “a dry measure”), from Akkadian 𒄥 (/⁠kurru⁠/), from Sumerian 𒄥 (gur, “a bundle of barley; standard unit of capacity”). Also found in Hebrew כֹּר (kōr), and in the meaning of a young donkey in Safaitic 𐪋𐪇 (kr /⁠korr⁠/) beside two asses pictured."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n36801","headword_ar":"كَرٌّ","root":"kr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A rope"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made in the form of a hoop"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by means of which one ascends a palm-tree;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) accord. to A'Obeyd, a name not applied to any other rope; and so, says Az, I have heard from the Arabs; it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made of the best of"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the fibres of the palm-tree called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liyf","text_ar":"لِيف"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thick rope;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) accord. to AO,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liyf","text_ar":"لِيف"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and of the outer covering"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qi$or","text_ar":"قِشْر"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portions of the racemes of the palm-tree called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Earajiyn","text_ar":"عَرَجِين"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion of the branch called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Easiyb","text_ar":"عَسِيب"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a rope, in general:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Th, K:) and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rope"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sheet"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a sail:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rope of a ship:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rope by which a ship is drawn:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qayod","text_ar":"قَيْد"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pair of shackles,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hobbles,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liyf","text_ar":"لِيف"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of palm-leaves:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kuruwrN","text_ar":"كُرُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, TA.)       -A2-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing that connects the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"two pieces of wood called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalifataAni","text_ar":"ظَلِفَتَانِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kind of camel's saddle called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHol","text_ar":"رَحْل"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and that enters"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is inserted"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into them:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ajorN","text_ar":"شَجْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$axorN","text_ar":"شَخْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leather, into which the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalifaAt","text_ar":"ظَلِفَات"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHol","text_ar":"رَحْل"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"enter; occupying the same place in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHol","text_ar":"رَحْل"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bidaAdaAni","text_ar":"بِدَادَانِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"have in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qatab","text_ar":"قَتَب"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"excepting that the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bdAdAn","text_ar":"بدادان"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"do not appear before the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalifap","text_ar":"ظَلِفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akoraArN","text_ar":"اَكْرَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","Th","K","S"]},{"entry_id":"n36802","headword_ar":"كُرٌّ","root":"kr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain measure of capacity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the people of El-'Irák,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for wheat;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"well known;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"consisting of six ass-loads,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) that is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sixty times the quantity called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qafiyz","text_ar":"قَفِيز"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Az, Mgh, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"accord. to the people of El-'Irák,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qfyz","text_ar":"قفيز"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being eight"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"makaAkiyk","text_ar":"مَكَاكِيك"},{"kind":"text","text":", [in the TA, six, but this is a mistake,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mak~uwk","text_ar":"مَكُّوك"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAE","text_ar":"صَاع"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and a half, which is three"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kiylajaAt","text_ar":"كِيلَجَات"},{"kind":"text","text":"; so that the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kur~","text_ar":"كُرّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to this reckoning, is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"twelve times the quantity called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wasoq","text_ar":"وَسْق"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Az, Mgh, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"each"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wsq","text_ar":"وسق"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being sixty times the quantity called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SAE","text_ar":"صاع"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Az, Mgh:) in the Kitáb Kudámeh, it is said that the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kur~","text_ar":"كُرّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmuEad~alu","text_ar":"المُعَدَّلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sixty times the quantity called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qfyz","text_ar":"قفيز"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qfyz","text_ar":"قفيز"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is ten"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEo$iraA='","text_ar":"اَعْشِرَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":": and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kur~","text_ar":"كُرّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alqanoqalu","text_ar":"القَنْقَلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"twice the quantity of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kur~ muEad~al","text_ar":"كُرّ مُعَدَّل"},{"kind":"text","text":", that is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qfyz","text_ar":"قفيز"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mEd~l","text_ar":"معدّل"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a hundred and twenty times the quantity of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qfyz","text_ar":"قفيز"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with this"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kr~","text_ar":"كرّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"are measured unripe dates and dried dates and also olives, in the districts of El-Basrah; and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qfyz","text_ar":"قفيز"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"used for measuring dates is twenty-five times the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riTol","text_ar":"رِطْل"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of Baghdád;"},{"kind":"text","text":"so that the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kur~u Alqanoqali","text_ar":"كُرُّ القَنْقَلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"three thousand times as much as the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rTl","text_ar":"رطل"},{"kind":"text","text":": and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kur~","text_ar":"كُرّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlhaA$imiY~u","text_ar":"الهَاشِمِىُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"third part of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mEd~l","text_ar":"معدّل"},{"kind":"text","text":", that is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"twenty times as much as the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qfyz","text_ar":"قفيز"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by the measure of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mEd~l","text_ar":"معدّل"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with this"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kur~","text_ar":"كُرّ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rice is measured:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kur~","text_ar":"كُرّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlhaAruwniY~u","text_ar":"الهَارُونِىُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"equal to them two"},{"kind":"text","text":"[but what these two are is not shown]: and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ahowaAziY~","text_ar":"اَهْوَازِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"equal to them two:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxotuwm","text_ar":"مَخْتُوم"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sixth part of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qfyz","text_ar":"قفيز"},{"kind":"text","text":": and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qfyz","text_ar":"قفيز"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tenth part of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jariyb","text_ar":"جَرِيب"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh:) or the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kur~","text_ar":"كُرّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"forty times as much as the quantity called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_irodab~","text_ar":"اـِرْدَبّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by the reckoning of the people of Egypt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as ISd says: (TA:) the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ikraAr","text_ar":"اـِكرَار"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Msb.) [It is app. connected with the Hebrew"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"כֹּר","text_ar":"כֹּר","orth_type":"plain"},{"kind":"text","text":", whence the Greek"},{"kind":"text","text":"ko/ros"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a measure containing, accord. to Josephus, six Attic medimni,) occurring in Luke xvi. 7.]"}],"source_refs":["Mgh","Msb","K","Az","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}